stork.feather

Class Stat

  • java.lang.Object
    • stork.feather.Stat

  • public class Stat
extends Object
    Metadata about a resource, including subresources if the resource is a directory. Many of the members of this class are determined on a best-effort basis, depending on the implementation, and should not be taken to be absolutely correct.
